~ interaction_2
Lighthouse Keeper: You're back?
MATE: You seem interesting.
Lighthouse Keeper: I was kind of harsh earlier, in fact now that I think about it, your question wasn't so out of place, we live in Butterfly Grove as you probably already know, when I told you "I'm the lighthouse keeper of the isle" what I truly meant is that I'm the lighthouse keeper of the nearby island, the one located south-west of Butterfly Grove, and yes Butterfly Grove is truly just the name of this main island.
